Release Notes for Version 3.12.3
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.12.3 is the 4th release in
the Errata Tool 3.12 development period. It closes [16 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes enhancements to batch functionality
which now allows set of advisories in a batch to be locked, and a number of
enhancements to Product Security workflow, UI, and Pub integration.

Additionally, during the 3.12.3 development period, an additional [3 bug
fixes][hotfixes] were shipped in 3.12.2.1.

